<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Can Ethereum Addresses Be Traced Back to the Real-World Identity of the User?</h3>



<p>Yes, Ethereum addresses can be traced back to the real-world identity of the user. This is because of the transparency of the blockchain, which allows anyone to view transactions and analyze patterns to uncover the identity behind an address.</p>



